The Burundi Bethel family
and the 83 publishers

00:52:28.749 --> 00:52:32.837 line:90% position:50% align:center
of the Bujumbura Gihosha Centre Congregation

00:52:32.837 --> 00:52:36.674 line:90% position:50% align:center
